{"tid":2379422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"輕度智障男機場集會被指鐳射筆襲警罪成 香淑嫻判監半年 旁聽人士難忍淚水 鼓譟不斷高呼「冇天理」","createTime":"2021-01-25T08:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T18:14:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":44,"dislike":197,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"e032424a197c207394ef9a95b57fe2d0ca928044","tid":2379422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13201&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=992321a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13201</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙田裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n#0813機場 #判刑<br />\n#襲警 #攻擊性武器 #鐳射筆<br />\n<br />\n區(27)‼️已還押15日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n第212章《侵害人身罪條例》第36條<br />\n被控於2019年8月13日，在機場一號客運大樓8樓離境大堂外，襲擊警員9085。<br />\n(2)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n第245章《公安條例》第33條<br />\n被控於同日在離境大堂外管有１支鐳射筆。<br />\n<br />\n裁決理由 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12813&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=1951fe87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12813</a>)<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n辯方先向法庭致歉，因打亂原定案件編排。辯方已向被告解釋２份精神科報告、１份心理報告及１份背景報告。被告清楚明白其內容。<br />\n<br />\n判刑：<br />\n控罪(1)：以３個月為量刑起點<br />\n控罪(2)：以６個月為量刑起點<br />\n<br />\n考慮到被告智力情況，根據李啟發案例，各項控罪給予１個月刑期扣減。２項控罪同期執行：<br />\n‼️總刑期為６個月‼️<br />\n<br />\n在場人士鼓譟，不斷高呼「冇天理」。被告母親聞判情緒非常激動，不住嚎啕大哭。旁聽席上各人聞判亦難忍淚水。<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"c642783953f04f4c2d321b9282f4d9897926731a","tid":2379422,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754d70166d4aeb903c9edcbfb82e2d13bf18f75a","tid":2379422,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7d0ee3dd15ffbe550aba3d851c4a9289f1ec6c","tid":2379422,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">無天理</span>"},{"pid":"a66b6f727247943429f3cb24e9d77ab961554e25","tid":2379422,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ab687b9d707c04ccb8afab4605c6aa604280e2","tid":2379422,"uid":44180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"1e43d4f9d63668050a0dedae89f55bc3eb767e4c","tid":2379422,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"a09312466f647b9a0d3824d3b22460b4054ab4e6","tid":2379422,"uid":196924,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"智障都入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f688003a5b0eeda0159cdcac781e1db3178e60","tid":2379422,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:26:25.000Z","msg":"就刑期上訴啦"},{"pid":"3e8667ab6e528140a2ab648feb59806874d90a08","tid":2379422,"uid":231480,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"quote":{"pid":"a09312466f647b9a0d3824d3b22460b4054ab4e6","tid":2379422,"uid":196924,"like":32