":"雷射筆襲警告得入其實真係好戇尻<br />\n雖然話已經判左唔少單<br />\n但其實真係好撚無稽<br />\n個官講得出警員眼睛沒有受傷實屬萬幸有冇廉恥？<br />\n再者狗果枝白燈仲勁啦 仲成尻日周圍射<br />\n話冇立場 公平公正真係天大既笑話"},{"pid":"684fa62d3e7d14866ffd7fb228dd2179a4639f99","tid":2379422,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"香港有法治呀<br />\n咁多呢啲法官點會冇法治啫<br />\n納稅法庭都有法治啦"},{"pid":"7ded323cfcce8a407c203b07521671dd9523db95","tid":2379422,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"港共賤種狗官我屌哂你地老母啊"},{"pid":"90de6271ac8529ad136bfbc6707e74df5320d305","tid":2379422,"uid":336429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e032424a197c207394ef9a95b57fe2d0ca928044","tid":2379422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13201&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=992321a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13201</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙田裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n#0813機場 #判刑<br />\n#襲警 #攻擊性武器 #鐳射筆<br />\n<br />\n區(27)‼️已還押15日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n第212章《侵害人身罪條例》第36條<br />\n被控於2019年8月13日，在機場一號客運大樓8樓離境大堂外，襲擊警員9085。<br />\n(2)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n第245章《公安條例》第33條<br />\n被控於同日在離境大堂外管有１支鐳射筆。<br />\n<br />\n裁決理由 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12813&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=1951fe87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12813</a>)<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n辯方先向法庭致歉，因打亂原定案件編排。辯方已向被告解釋２份精神科報告、１份心理報告及１份背景報告。被告清楚明白其內容。<br />\n<br />\n判刑：<br />\n控罪(1)：以３個月為量刑起點<br />\n控罪(2)：以６個月為量刑起點<br />\n<br />\n考慮到被告智力情況，根據李啟發案例，各項控罪給予１個月刑期扣減。２項控罪同期執行：<br />\n‼️總刑期為６個月‼️<br />\n<br />\n在場人士鼓譟，不斷高呼「冇天理」。被告母親聞判情緒非常激動，不住嚎啕大哭。旁聽席上各人聞判亦難忍淚水。<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"唉又沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個等食花生睇光時攬炒巴一齊互炒,班低能condom坐幾耐wfc啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5caac72afc420725b143d8ba6496cf48f3d42fa7","tid":2379422,"uid":190591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81040c331816d1a2e76bfb04573e86105253bf22","tid":2379422,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a5e2b3cf0d980a1223e0bf7260b81775aa7c16","tid":2379422,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"cctoy手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6157ae6e0aeda57b99d7a3c745cf889fddccf95","tid":2379422,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef951c2b05630001e7712176e8c0a52c24c81518","tid":2379422,"uid":177578,"like":5,"dislike":21,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"手joke襲驚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"Joke你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"17e0c95f7e6b31ae26d339